<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport" />
  <title>Schools — Classic Academy</title>

  <meta
    content="Search schools, compare profiles, view subjects and performance, then apply online with Classic Academy."
    name="description" />
  <meta
    content="school search, school admissions, school profiles, online application, Classic Academy"
    name="keywords" />
  <meta content="index,follow,max-snippet:-1,max-image-preview:large,max-video-preview:-1" name="robots" />
  <meta content="#4a90e2" name="theme-color" />
  <meta content="Classic Academy" name="application-name" />
  <meta content="telephone=no" name="format-detection" />

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect" />
  <link crossorigin="" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    :root {
      --primary: #4a90e2;
      --accent: #d97800;
      --highlight: #009f8b;
      --ink: #0f172a;
      --muted: #475569;
      --page-pad: clamp(1rem, 4vw, 6rem);
      --section-gap: clamp(1.2rem, 2.6vw, 2rem);
      --shadow2: 0 18px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, .12);
      --radius: 22px;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background: #e0f7fa;
      color: #333;
      overflow-x: clip;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
      padding-top: 112px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      body {
        padding-top: 102px;
      }
    }

    #loader {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: #e0f7fa;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      z-index: 9999;
      padding: 1.2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .academylogo {
      width: min(220px, 70vw);
    }

    .academylogo img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }

    .loader {
      position: relative;
      width: 18px;
      height: 28px;
      perspective: 500px;
      animation: flip 2s infinite;
    }

    .loader:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .loader:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
    .loader:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
    .loader:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }

    .face {
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      backface-visibility: hidden;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .front { background: var(--primary); }
    .back {
      background: #d35400;
      transform: rotateY(180deg);
    }

    @keyframes flip {
      0%, 100% { transform: rotateY(0deg); }
      50% { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
    }

    .header {
      position: fixed;
      top: 14px;
      left: var(--page-pad);
      right: var(--page-pad);
      padding: .65rem .85rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .70);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .78);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 46px rgba(15, 23, 42, .10);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: .8rem;
      z-index: 2000;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .75rem;
      min-width: 0;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .brand-mark {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, .10);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .85);
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .brand-txt {
      display: grid;
      line-height: 1.05;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .brand-name {
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -.02em;
      color: var(--ink);
      white-space: nowrap;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
    }

    .brand-sub {
      font-size: .86rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      white-space: nowrap;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
    }

    .navbar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .35rem;
    }

    .navbar a {
      padding: .55rem .75rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: #1d4ed8;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      transition: background .2s ease, transform .2s ease, color .2s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .navbar a:hover {
      background: rgba(74, 144, 226, .10);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .nav-pill {
      border: 1px solid rgba(74, 144, 226, .35);
      background: rgba(74, 144, 226, .10);
      color: #0f172a !important;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .nav-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .55rem;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: .45rem;
      padding: 0.72rem 1rem;
      background-color: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--primary);
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 800;
      transition: background-color .25s ease, transform .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      user-select: none;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(74, 144, 226, .18);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: transparent;
      color: var(--primary);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(15, 23, 42, .12);
    }

    .btn.ghost {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, .12);
      color: var(--ink);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, .08);
    }

    .btn.ghost:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .88);
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .btn-sm {
      padding: .55rem .8rem !important;
      font-size: .95rem !important;
      box-shadow: none !important;
    }

    .menu-btn {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, .12);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .78);
      display: none;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, .08);
    }

    .menu-btn i {
      color: var(--ink);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .brand-sub { display: none; }
      .menu-btn { display: inline-flex; }

      .navbar {
        position: absolute;
        top: calc(100% + .65rem);
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        margin: 0 .25rem;
        padding: .75rem;
        background: rgba(74, 144, 226, .96);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .35);
        border-radius: 20px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        display: grid;
        gap: .4rem;
        transform: translateY(-8px);
        opacity: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
        transition: transform .2s ease, opacity .2s ease;
      }

      .navbar.active {
        transform: translateY(0);
        opacity: 1;
        pointer-events: auto;
      }

      .navbar a {
        color: #fff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: .85rem .85rem;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .08);
      }

      .navbar a:hover {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .14);
        transform: none;
        color: #fff;
      }

      .nav-pill {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .18);
        border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .35);
        color: #fff !important;
      }
    }

    .schools-page {
      position: relative;
      margin: 0 var(--page-pad);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      border-radius: calc(var(--radius) + 6px);
      overflow: hidden;
      background:
        radial-gradient(900px 420px at 10% 15%, rgba(74, 144, 226, .18), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(760px 420px at 90% 0%, rgba(217, 120, 0, .12), transparent 55%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, .75), rgba(255, 255, 255, .55));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .65);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow2);
    }

    .schools-shell {
      padding: clamp(1rem, 2.2vw, 1.35rem);
    }

    .schools-hero {
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: clamp(1rem, 2.3vw, 1.4rem);
      background:
        radial-gradient(920px 320px at 10% 10%, rgba(74, 144, 226, .24), transparent 62%),
        radial-gradient(800px 300px at 90% 0%, rgba(0, 159, 139, .18), transparent 55%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, .82), rgba(255, 255, 255, .58));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .78);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(15, 23, 42, .10);
    }

    .schools-kicker {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .55rem;
      padding: .45rem .75rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .70);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .82);
      color: #1b2a4e;
      font-weight: 800;
      width: fit-content;
    }

    .schools-hero h1 {
      margin-top: .85rem;
      font-size: clamp(1.55rem, 2.55vw, 2.35rem);
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -.02em;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .schools-hero h1 span {
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .schools-sub {
      margin-top: .65rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 650;
      max-width: 58rem;
    }

    .schools-stats {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: .6rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .schools-stat {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .6rem;
      padding: .55rem .75rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .62);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .80);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(15, 23, 42, .06);
      color: #1b2a4e;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .schools-stat span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .schools-form {
      margin-top: var(--section-gap);
    }

    .schools-controls {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr .8fr .8fr .8fr auto;
      gap: .75rem;
      margin-top: var(--section-gap);
    }

    .schools-control {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .65rem;
      padding: .75rem .85rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .86);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(15, 23, 42, .06);
    }

    .schools-control i {
      color: rgba(15, 23, 42, .55);
    }

    .schools-control input,
    .schools-control select {
      width: 100%;
      border: none;
      outline: none;
      background: transparent;
      font: inherit;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .schools-control select {
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .schools-check {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: .55rem;
      padding: .75rem .95rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .86);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(15, 23, 42, .06);
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--ink);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .schools-check input {
      width: auto;
    }

    .schools-chips {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: .6rem;
      margin-top: .9rem;
    }

    .schools-chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .55rem;
      padding: .55rem .75rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, .10);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .70);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .schools-chip i {
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .schools-chip.is-active {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--highlight));
      border-color: transparent;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .schools-chip.is-active i {
      color: #fff;
    }

    .schools-empty {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .86);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(15, 23, 42, .06);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .schools-empty-icon {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      margin: 0 auto .5rem;
      background: rgba(74, 144, 226, .12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(74, 144, 226, .18);
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .schools-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: .9rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      padding-bottom: .35rem;
    }

    .school-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .82);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .88);
      border-radius: calc(var(--radius) - 2px);
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, .08);
      transition: transform .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .school-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 46px rgba(15, 23, 42, .12);
    }

    .school-cover {
      height: 120px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a90e2, #009f8b);
    }

    .school-cover::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(600px 220px at 70% 10%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.22), transparent 60%);
      opacity: .95;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .school-cover img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    .school-avatar {
      position: absolute;
      left: 14px;
      bottom: -22px;
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .92);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .92);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #1b2a4e;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(15, 23, 42, .12);
      z-index: 2;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .school-avatar img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    .school-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: 12px;
      right: 12px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .45rem;
      padding: .4rem .6rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: .82rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .30);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .45);
      color: #fff;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .school-badge.ok {
      background: rgba(236, 253, 243, .92);
      border-color: rgba(187, 247, 208, .95);
      color: #15803d;
      backdrop-filter: none;
    }

    .school-body {
      padding: 2.1rem .95rem .95rem;
    }

    .school-top {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: .7rem;
    }

    .school-name {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: -.01em;
      line-height: 1.2;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .school-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .45rem;
      padding: .38rem .6rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .70);
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, .10);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: .82rem;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .school-pill i {
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .school-tagline {
      margin-top: .55rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 650;
      font-size: .92rem;
      min-height: 2.2rem;
    }

    .school-meta {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: .65rem;
      margin-top: .6rem;
      color: rgba(15, 23, 42, .85);
      font-weight: 750;
      font-size: .86rem;
    }

    .school-meta i {
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .school-kpis {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: .55rem;
      margin-top: .75rem;
    }

    .school-kpi {
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, .08);
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, .03);
      padding: .55rem .6rem;
    }

    .school-kpi .v {
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #1b2a4e;
      font-size: .92rem;
    }

    .school-kpi .l {
      margin-top: .15rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: .75rem;
    }

    .school-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: .55rem;
      margin-top: .75rem;
    }

    .schools-btn {
      padding: .55rem .8rem !important;
      border-radius: 999px !important;
      font-size: .92rem !important;
    }

    .pagination {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: .6rem;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .page-link {
      padding: .65rem .9rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .82);
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, .08);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .page-link.active {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--highlight));
      color: #fff;
      border-color: transparent;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-radius: 25px;
      margin: 2rem var(--page-pad);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      gap: 0;
    }

    .footer div {
      margin: 1rem;
      flex: 1 1 220px;
      min-width: 220px;
    }

    .footer h4 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .footer ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .footer ul li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .footer ul li a {
      color: #333;
    }

    .footer ul li a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    #toTopBtn {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 30px;
      right: 30px;
      background-color: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      display: none;
      z-index: 1000;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    #toTopBtn:hover {
      transform: scale(1.08);
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .schools-controls {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }

      .schools-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .schools-controls {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .schools-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .header,
      .schools-page,
      .footer,
      .navbar {
        backdrop-filter: none !important;
      }

      .header {
        box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, .10);
      }

      .schools-page {
        box-shadow: 0 16px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, .10);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="loader">
    <div class="academylogo">
      <img alt="Classic Academy logo" src="/img/academylogo.png" />
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:10px;">
      <div class="loader"><div class="face front"></div><div class="face back"></div></div>
      <div class="loader"><div class="face front"></div><div class="face back"></div></div>
      <div class="loader"><div class="face front"></div><div class="face back"></div></div>
      <div class="loader"><div class="face front"></div><div class="face back"></div></div>
      <div class="loader"><div class="face front"></div><div class="face back"></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <header class="header" id="siteHeader">
    <a aria-label="Classic Academy Home" class="brand" href="/">
      <img alt="Classic Academy logo" class="brand-mark" src="/img/academylogo.png" />
      <div class="brand-txt">
        <span class="brand-name">Classic Academy</span>
        <span class="brand-sub">School management + admissions</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <nav aria-label="Primary" class="navbar">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/about">About</a>
      <a href="/services">Features</a>
      <a href="/#testimonials">Benefits</a>
      <a href="/#contact">Contact</a>
      <a class="nav-pill" href="/#pricing">Join Today</a>
      <a class="nav-pill" href="/login">Sign In</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="nav-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-sm" href="/schedule"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check"></i> Book Demo</a>
      <button aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Open menu" class="menu-btn" id="menu-btn" type="button">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
      </button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section aria-label="Search Schools" class="schools-page">
    <div class="schools-shell">
      <div class="schools-hero">
        <div class="schools-kicker">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i> Search • Compare • Apply Online
        </div>

        <h1>Find a School <span>Powered by Classic Academy</span></h1>

        <p class="schools-sub">
          Search schools, compare subjects and performance, view galleries, see awards, then apply directly online.
        </p>

        <div class="schools-stats">
          <div class="schools-stat">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-school"></i> <%= totalAll %> <span>listed schools</span>
          </div>
          <div class="schools-stat">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Trusted <span>public profiles</span>
          </div>
          <div class="schools-stat">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-file-circle-plus"></i> Online applications <span>fast &amp; simple</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <form class="schools-form" method="GET" action="/schools" role="search" id="schoolsFilterForm">
        <input type="hidden" name="chip" id="schoolsChipInput" value="<%= chip || 'all' %>" />
        <input type="hidden" name="page" value="1" />

        <div class="schools-controls">
          <label class="schools-control">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
            <input
              autocomplete="off"
              id="schoolsQ"
              name="q"
              placeholder="Search school name, city, subject (e.g. Science, ICT)..."
              type="search"
              value="<%= q || '' %>" />
          </label>

          <label class="schools-control">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i>
            <select id="schoolsCity" name="city">
              <option value="">All cities</option>
              <% (cities || []).forEach(function(c) { %>
                <option value="<%= c %>" <%= city === c ? 'selected' : '' %>><%= c %></option>
              <% }) %>
            </select>
          </label>

          <label class="schools-control">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-building-columns"></i>
            <select id="schoolsType" name="type">
              <option value="">All types</option>
              <% (types || []).forEach(function(t) { %>
                <option value="<%= t %>" <%= type === t ? 'selected' : '' %>><%= t %></option>
              <% }) %>
            </select>
          </label>

          <label class="schools-control">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-wide-short"></i>
            <select id="schoolsSort" name="sort">
              <option value="rank" <%= sort === 'rank' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Sort: Recommended</option>
              <option value="students" <%= sort === 'students' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Students (high → low)</option>
              <option value="subjects" <%= (sort === 'subjects' || sort === 'programs') ? 'selected' : '' %>>Subjects high to low</option>
              <option value="name" <%= sort === 'name' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Name (A → Z)</option>
            </select>
          </label>

          <label class="schools-check">
            <input id="schoolsVerified" name="verified" type="checkbox" value="1" <%= verified ? 'checked' : '' %> />
            Verified
          </label>
        </div>

        <div aria-label="Quick filters" class="schools-chips">
          <button class="schools-chip <%= (!chip || chip === 'all') ? 'is-active' : '' %>" data-chip="all" type="button">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i> All
          </button>
          <button class="schools-chip <%= chip === 'verified' ? 'is-active' : '' %>" data-chip="verified" type="button">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Verified
          </button>
          <button class="schools-chip <%= chip === 'boarding' ? 'is-active' : '' %>" data-chip="boarding" type="button">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-bed"></i> Boarding
          </button>
          <button class="schools-chip <%= chip === 'day' ? 'is-active' : '' %>" data-chip="day" type="button">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-sun"></i> Day
          </button>
          <button class="schools-chip <%= chip === 'science' ? 'is-active' : '' %>" data-chip="science" type="button">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-flask"></i> Science
          </button>
          <button class="schools-chip <%= chip === 'ict' ? 'is-active' : '' %>" data-chip="ict" type="button">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-laptop-code"></i> ICT
          </button>
        </div>
      </form>

      <% if (!items || !items.length) { %>
        <div aria-live="polite" class="schools-empty">
          <div class="schools-empty-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-face-frown"></i></div>
          <b>No schools match your search</b>
          <p>Try changing filters, remove chips, or search a different city/subject.</p>
        </div>
      <% } else { %>
        <div aria-label="School results" class="schools-grid">
          <% items.forEach(function(item) {
            const branding = item.settings?.branding || {};
            const profile = item.settings?.profile || {};
            const stats = profile.stats || {};
            const location = profile.location || {};
            const contact = profile.contact || {};
            const awards = profile.awards || [];
            const rating = profile.ratingSummary || {};
            const initials = (profile.shortName || item.name || 'S').slice(0, 2).toUpperCase();
            const applyHref = profile.admissions?.applyUrl || ('https://' + item.code + '.' + baseDomain + '/apply');
          %>
            <article
              class="school-card"
              data-url="/schools/<%= item.code %>"
              tabindex="0"
              role="link">

              <div class="school-cover">
                <% if (branding.coverUrl) { %>
                  <img src="<%= branding.coverUrl %>" alt="<%= item.name %> cover" />
                <% } %>

                <div class="school-avatar">
                  <% if (branding.logoUrl) { %>
                    <img src="<%= branding.logoUrl %>" alt="<%= item.name %> logo" />
                  <% } else { %>
                    <%= initials %>
                  <% } %>
                </div>

                <div class="school-badge <%= profile.verified ? 'ok' : '' %>">
                  <% if (profile.verified) { %>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Verified
                  <% } else { %>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i> Listed
                  <% } %>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="school-body">
                <div class="school-top">
                  <h3 class="school-name"><%= item.name %></h3>
                  <span class="school-pill">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-building-columns"></i>
                    <%= profile.type || 'School' %>
                  </span>
                </div>

                <div class="school-tagline">
                  <%= profile.tagline || 'Explore this school profile on Classic Academy.' %>
                </div>

                <div class="school-meta">
                  <span>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i>
                    <%= location.city || 'N/A' %><%= location.country ? ', ' + location.country : '' %>
                  </span>

                  <% if (profile.system) { %>
                    <span>
                      <i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i>
                      <%= profile.system %>
                    </span>
                  <% } %>

                  <% if (contact.phone) { %>
                    <span>
                      <i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i>
                      <%= contact.phone %>
                    </span>
                  <% } %>

                  <% if (rating.count) { %>
                    <span>
                      <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                      <%= rating.avg || 0 %> / 5
                    </span>
                  <% } %>
                </div>

                <div class="school-kpis">
                  <div class="school-kpi">
                    <div class="v"><%= Number(stats.students || 0).toLocaleString() %></div>
                    <div class="l">Students</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="school-kpi">
                    <div class="v"><%= Number(stats.subjects ?? stats.programs ?? 0).toLocaleString() %></div>
                    <div class="l">Subjects</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="school-kpi">
                    <div class="v"><%= Number(awards.length || 0).toLocaleString() %></div>
                    <div class="l">Awards</div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="school-actions">
                  <a class="btn schools-btn" href="/schools/<%= item.code %>">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-id-card"></i> View Profile
                  </a>

                  <a class="btn ghost schools-btn" href="<%= applyHref %>">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-file-circle-plus"></i> Apply
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
          <% }) %>
        </div>

        <% if (pages > 1) { %>
          <div class="pagination">
            <% for (let i = 1; i <= pages; i++) { %>
              <a
                class="page-link <%= i === page ? 'active' : '' %>"
                href="/schools?<%= new URLSearchParams({
                  q: q || '',
                  city: city || '',
                  type: type || '',
                  chip: chip || 'all',
                  verified: verified ? '1' : '',
                  sort: sort || 'rank',
                  page: String(i)
                }).toString() %>">
                <%= i %>
              </a>
            <% } %>
          </div>
        <% } %>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div>
      <h4>About Us</h4>
      <p>We are excited to introduce our upcoming Classic Academy Plans, where schools will be categorized</p>
      <a href="https://play.google.com/store" rel="noopener" target="_blank">
        <img alt="Google Play" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/78/Google_Play_Store_badge_EN.svg"
          style="height: 50px; width: 150px" />
      </a>
      <a href="https://apps.apple.com/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">
        <img alt="Download on the App Store"
          src="https://developer.apple.com/assets/elements/badges/download-on-the-app-store.svg"
          style="height: 50px;" />
      </a>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4>Learn about our mission</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/about">Our Story</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services">What We Offer</a></li>
        <li><a href="/plan?plan=standard">Plans &amp; Pricing</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog?slug=increase-admissions">Press resources</a></li>
        <li><a href="/careers">Careers</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4>Get help with your account</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/contact">Customer Support</a></li>
        <li><a href="/schedule">Book a Demo</a></li>
        <li><a href="/faq">FAQ</a></li>
        <li><a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><a href="/terms">Terms</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4>Join our school community</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/schools">Find Schools</a></li>
        <li><a href="/admissions">Admissions</a></li>
        <li><a href="/search">Search</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog?slug=increase-admissions">Blog</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/HRGoS3fMZoZGgXbz1HDw6a?mode=gi_t" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Join whatsapp group</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <button aria-label="Scroll to top" id="toTopBtn" type="button">↑</button>

  <script src="/pages/schools.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
